name: Waiting
description:
"Waiting is crucial to succes" — on the most cliche things you can hear.
But that what I've learned in my mistakes during intense december of 2021, as i jumped into the NFT world. You should HOLD! 

Photo was taken in Venice on 26 of November 2021.
On a photo there is an old man in a hat. The man is waiting for Vaporetti. 

HODL. 
xxx
